            /
				Gets an array of ImapResponse objects representing all responses from the IMAP server applicable to this event.


If a multi-line response is expected from the server, iterate through this collection to access
				each response. If a single line response is expected from the server, access Responses[0] or simply
				access the ImapResponseEventArgs.Response property, which contains the first response received.
			Returns an array of ImapResponse objects.


